        <h3>Your dashboard looks complete. But most e-commerce analytics have gaps that don't show up until you go looking.</h3>
        <p>Most e-commerce brands we audit are making site decisions based on data they've never had reason to question. Revenue tracking that's missing part of the funnel. Conversion events firing on the wrong page. Session data that looks clean until you pull on one thread.</p>
